  "title": "Operations Coordinator (Freight forwarding) [Fort Canning | 5 days | up to $3200] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Operations Coordinator (Freight forwarding)</strong></h3><p><strong>5 days, 9am- 5.30pm</strong></p><p><strong>Address: Clemenceau Avenue, UE Square Singapore 239920 (Fort Canning)</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $3000 -$3200</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Liaise effectively with subcontractors, carriers, overseas agents, internal departments and clients to ensure timely and accurate shipment execution.</li><li>Provide regular updates to customers regarding shipment status, schedules, and any changes to arrangements.</li><li>Coordinate collection and delivery schedules with sub-contractors, including warehouse handling and cargo readiness.</li><li>Work closely with carriers to manage Bill of Lading (BL) issuance and collection and oversee payment arrangements.</li><li>Manage end-to-end operational tasks across import/export shipments, cross-border trucking, and cross-trade movements.</li><li>Prepare and process customs declarations in compliance with regulatory requirements.</li><li>Generate accurate billing and invoices, ensuring completion before monthly financial cut-off dates.</li><li>Maintain operational records and ensure data accuracy in internal systems.</li><li>Support continuous improvement initiatives to enhance service delivery and cost efficiency.</li><li>Collaborate with business development, sales and indoor sales team to resolve shipment issues and improve client satisfaction.</li><li>Assist in vendor performance reviews and contribute to operational reporting when needed</li><li>Contributes to team effort by accomplishing related results as needed</li><li>To perform other duties and tasks as assigned</li><li>Adhere to all company policies in areas of Compliance, HSSE&Q, Code of Business Conduct, Employee Handbook</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>At least 2 years of relevant work experience in the <strong>freight forwarding industry</strong></li><li>Must be familiar with Microsoft Word and Excel</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
